        "created_at": "2019-03-25T15:49:43.511Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I can see the appeal of making changes to the API simultaneously, but I don\u2019t think that this feature will be able to land in time for that to happen. It\u2019s something that I think requires some discussion to make sure that we\u2019re happy with what we end up with, but it\u2019s not currently in the priority list for things to be changed in 6.1, and I don\u2019t believe we intend to add much else to that release that\u2019s not currently in the roadmap for it.</p>\n<p>My hope is that this won\u2019t be too big of a deal API-wise, though, because this proposed feature would be an addition rather than a change.</p>",
